description: Create a dramatic AI poster of a superhero using a double-exposure effect. The right side of the face is realistic and detailed, while the left side blends into abstract blue tones with shattered glass textures and urban city elements. A glowing red silhouette of skyscrapers, including the Empire State Building, fades into the lower half of the portrait, symbolizing the heroâ€™s bond with the city. Designed in a red and blue color scheme with cinematic lighting, sharp details, and a futuristic poster style.

AI prompt for an 8K cinematic horror portrait. The subject holds a lit lighter close to his face, the orange-blue flame illuminating his sweaty skin with dramatic contrast. His expression is tense, eyes locked straight ahead. In the darkness behind him, a horror character of your choice whispers in his ear, half-concealed by shadows. The lighting creates a chilling, film-grade atmosphere perfect for poster or concept art generation.

AI prompt for a photorealistic portrait of a man in black streetwear with a massive black smoke demon behind him. Features dramatic lighting, cinematic style, and hyper-realistic details for dark fantasy character art.
AI prompt for a hyper-realistic cinematic portrait. Creates an image of a person in red streetwear with a large red smoke demon behind them, using a face reference photo. Dramatic low-key lighting.

An AI prompt to create a ultra-realistic, cinematic black and white portrait. It uses your uploaded photo to generate a likeness, adding a haunting shadow entity made of swirling black smoke with glowing eyes in a moody, high-contrast scene.

AI prompt to create a surreal fashion portrait in a public restroom. You stand in all-black streetwear while flat, graphic turquoise cartoon creatures interact with the stalls and environment, creating a mixed-media editorial look in 9:16 format.

AI prompt to transform your photo into a cinematic dark fantasy anime anti-hero. Features glowing red magma veins on the face, one bright red eye, a monochromatic style, and a sinister expression, rendered in hyper-realistic 8K quality.

AI prompt to blend a photorealistic portrait of you with a 2D cartoon monkey sitting on your baseball cap. Creates a 'Who Framed Roger Rabbit' style image with a weary, sad mood, shallow depth of field, and a blurred indoor background.

AI prompt for an ultra-realistic luxury portrait on a city sidewalk. You wear a black pinstripe outfit, with a translucent 'See No Evil' ghost and a purple demon aura behind you, creating a mysterious, high-fashion cinematic scene.

AI prompt creates photorealistic characters breaking out of manga panels. Dynamic running pose with dramatic lighting. Black-and-white comic background with 9:16 vertical format. Perfect for character art and portraits.

AI prompt creates psychological horror scenes with mirror reflections showing dual personalities. Uses your reference photo for accurate facial matching. Features teal dark tones, foggy atmosphere, and dramatic 9:16 vertical composition.

Generate a surreal conceptual artwork where thousands of tiny people form a giant side-profile face that dissolves into stone, moss, and roots. Features dramatic top-down lighting and minimal white background.

Generate an ultra-realistic medium shot of a person sitting on a brown leather sofa atop a mountain, surrounded by foggy hills. Perfect for surreal art, conceptual photography, or dreamlike personal portraits.
Generate a haunting conceptual portrait of a single illuminated figure surrounded by a faceless crowd in fabric hoods. Perfect for dystopian art, social commentary, or powerful personal storytelling.

Generate a dreamlike cinematic portrait of yourself seated on fluffy clouds in a vintage tailored suit. Perfect for luxury fashion editorials, surreal personal branding, or fine art photography with a timeless feel.
